\par }{\b\fs24\cgrid0 Ivy Siege}{\fs24\cgrid0  (Enchantment)
\par 
\par Sphere: Plant
\par Range: 90 yards
\par Components: V, S, M
\par Duration: 6 turns
\par Casting Time: 9
\par Area of Effect: 1 building or similar structure
\par Saving Throw: Special
\par 
