\par }{\i\fs24\cgrid0 The following represents a summation of information on druids from the AD&D Original Edition }{\fs24\cgrid0 Player's Handbook}{\i\fs24\cgrid0  and the }{\fs24\cgrid0 Unearthed Arcana}{\i\fs24\cgrid0 
